Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.09,0:22:08.51,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}Be my power,future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.60,0:22:18.19,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要喚出情感之名 則無休無止無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.23,0:22:26.28,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神傳來呼喚 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.28,0:22:28.11,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:29.36,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:32.95,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無論光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:36.83,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如緊湊相連的拼圖零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:41.08,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.50,0:22:45.34,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.34,0:22:50.01,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}終將指引我們走向所堅信的邂逅
